item.title: CVE-2020-5396|2024-08-04T08:30:24.241Z -- vmware%20tanzu -- vmware%20tanzu%20gemfire%20for%20vms
item.description: VMware GemFire versions prior to 9.10.0, 9.9.2, 9.8.7, and 9.7.6, and VMware Tanzu GemFire for VMs versions prior to 1.11.1 and 1.10.2, when deployed without a SecurityManager, contain a JMX service available which contains an insecure default configuration. This allows a malicious user to create an MLet mbean leading to remote code execution.
